description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of part 3, part 5, part 6, part 7, part 8, part 10 storey building to provide 82 residential units (comprising 22 x1 bed, 33 x 2 bed, 18 x 3 bed and 9 x 4 bed units) and 5,908 sqm of commercial floor space. (5,603 sqm B1 use, 305 sqm A3 (food/drink) use) together with provision of 46 parking spaces and 70 cycle spaces at basement level. (Amended version of scheme approval under ref:2004/2702)
